From the root of myproject, run:

python mcp_server.py


Or for production:
fastmcp run mcp_server.py

For DOcker

# Dockerfile

FROM python:3.11-slim

WORKDIR /app

COPY . .

RUN pip install -r requirements.txt

CMD ["fastmcp", "run", "mcp_server.py"]


Then build and run:
docker build -t myproject-mcp .
docker run -d -p 8080:8080 myproject-mcp